## Sprint 4: Webhooks ✅

### Architecture

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Merchant DB
    participant Webhook Dispatcher
    participant Kafka (payment.events)
    participant Payment Service
    
    Payment Service->>Kafka (payment.events): publish(PaymentEvent)
    Kafka (payment.events)-->>Webhook Dispatcher: consume(PaymentEvent)
    Webhook Dispatcher->>Merchant DB: find merchant details
    Webhook Dispatcher->>Webhook Dispatcher: compute HMAC-SHA256 signature
    Webhook Dispatcher->>Merchant API: POST payload + signature
    Webhook Dispatcher->>Merchant DB: Persist WebhookEvent (status)
```

### Files Created
