| [service/PaymentEventPublisher.java](file:///d:/DEVS/ANTIGRAVITY/FINTECH/FinPay/apps/api/payment-service/src/main/java/com/finpay/payment/service/PaymentEventPublisher.java) | Kafka producer for payment status changes |
| [consumer/PaymentEventConsumer.java](file:///d:/DEVS/ANTIGRAVITY/FINTECH/FinPay/apps/api/webhook-service/src/main/java/com/finpay/webhook/consumer/PaymentEventConsumer.java) | Kafka listener intercepting payment events |
