### API Usage (once running with Docker infra)

```bash
# Create a payment
curl -X POST http://localhost:8081/v1/payments \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "amount": 5000,
    "currency": "eur",
    "method": "CARD",
    "merchantId": "<uuid>",
    "idempotencyKey": "pay_abc123",
    "description": "Test payment"
  }'
```
